data.description: This is a lovely 1/2 duplex home that has a split rail fence in front.  It is a Monterrey 2 bedrooms & 2 baths style cottage with plantation shutters and a sliding glass door that leads to an enclosed sun room. The sun room looks on a green belt. The kitchen has beautiful counter tops, electric free-standing stove and a refrigerator. This home is on the maintained landscaping program, so you don't have to spend time cutting the grass!  Sellers will be giving paint allowance so new buyer can choose colors.
